name: PHImageRequestOptionsVersion
desc: Options for requesting an image asset with or without adjustments, used by the version property.

items.name: case current
items.desc: Request the most recent version of the image asset (the one that reflects all edits).

items.name: case unadjusted
items.desc: Request a version of the image asset without adjustments.

items.name: case original
items.desc: Request the original, highest-fidelity version of the image asset.
